%% KubeRay Operator - Data Flow Diagram
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / Data Scientist
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Webhook as Mutating Webhook<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant Operator as KubeRay Operator<br/>(controller-runtime)
    participant HeadPod as Ray Head Pod<br/>8265/TCP HTTP
    participant RBAC as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Gateway as data-science-gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant CertMgr as cert-manager<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Workers as Ray Worker Pods

    Note over User,Workers: Flow 1: RayCluster Creation with Authentication

    User->>K8sAPI: Create RayCluster CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: Validate/Mutate RayCluster<br/>TLS (serving cert)
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Admission Response
    K8sAPI->>Operator: Watch event (RayCluster)
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Head Pod + kube-rbac-proxy sidecar<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Worker Pods
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create head-svc (ClusterIP)
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create HTTPRoute in platform namespace
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create ReferenceGrant in cluster namespace

    Note over User,Workers: Flow 2: Authenticated Dashboard Access (Gateway API)

    User->>Gateway: GET /ray/{ns}/{cluster}<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+, Bearer Token
    Gateway->>RBAC: Forward to kube-rbac-proxy<br/>HTTPS/8443 TLS
    RBAC->>K8sAPI: SubjectAccessReview<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+
    K8sAPI-->>RBAC: Authorization Result
    RBAC->>HeadPod: Proxy to Ray Dashboard<br/>HTTP/8265 localhost
    HeadPod-->>RBAC: Dashboard Response
    RBAC-->>Gateway: Proxied Response
    Gateway-->>User: Dashboard HTML

    Note over User,Workers: Flow 3: RayJob Submission

    User->>K8sAPI: Create RayJob CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>Operator: Watch event (RayJob)
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create/Reuse RayCluster
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create K8s Job (submitter)
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: Job created
    Note right of Operator: Submitter Job Pod
    Operator->>HeadPod: Submit job via Dashboard API<br/>HTTP/8265

    Note over User,Workers: Flow 4: mTLS Certificate Provisioning

    Operator->>CertMgr: Create SelfSigned Issuer
    Operator->>CertMgr: Create CA Certificate
    CertMgr-->>Operator: CA Secret provisioned
    Operator->>CertMgr: Create CA Issuer
    Operator->>CertMgr: Create Head/Worker Certificates
    CertMgr-->>Operator: TLS Secrets provisioned
    HeadPod->>HeadPod: Mount TLS secrets
    Workers->>Workers: Mount TLS secrets
    HeadPod->>Workers: mTLS communication<br/>6379/TCP cert-manager CA
